originalText.text:
Don't even consider...

The worse CPA ever. They did my tax returns in such unprofessional way that resulted in liens on my bank account

I hired Diza and Ildi to work on my taxes. Although I provide all relevant info, my Tax was filed wrong. It took me weeks to get their attention to their the wrongful actions... although they claimed all was fixed and resolved I found a few months later the IRS put a lean on my accounts

This obviously was very frustrating, not only the fact I needed to keep following up on them to fix it but also the negligence way they handled my case that eventually brought damages to my credit...

No matter what they say, don't trust them or their work - believe me, I'm not the only one...

Stay away
